Add hash table index for O(1) palette lookup by ID.

ptyxis_palette_lookup() previously performed O(n) linear scan through
the list model with g_list_model_get_item() ref/unref overhead per
iteration. Add a GHashTable that maps palette IDs to PtyxisPalette
objects, populated on initialization and kept in sync via items-changed.

The items-changed callback uses position/removed/added parameters:
- removed > 0: full rebuild (removed IDs are no longer accessible)
- removed == 0: incremental insert of [position, position+added) only

Index: src/ptyxis-palette.c
--- src/ptyxis-palette.c.orig
+++ src/ptyxis-palette.c
